# Cloudflare Pages response headers (https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/headers/)
# Conservative hardening only: no Content-Security-Policy (would need tuning for
# the Meta Pixel / GA / Shopify), and no X-Frame-Options (so the diagnostic can
# still be embedded on kpcnotesmt.com if you ever want that).
/*
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: geolocation=(), microphone=(), camera=()
